Command + down = next line
command + D = selects the same word found down the code
command + right = goes to the end of the line
command + \ = creates a sided window

control + up = separate the windows
control + down = shows me folders and highlights the window

option + up or down = brings the code line upwards or downwards
option + shift + f = format entire code
option + shift + down = copies the code undernieth the original code
shift + tab = ident left
lorem + tab = whole text
lorem*100 = whole text with 100 words

